itemListElement.name: Private Shopping Tour from Seattle to Seattle Premium Outlets

name: Private Shopping Tour from Seattle to Seattle Premium Outlets
description:
Comfortable Roundtrip Tour from your hotel in Seattle to Seattle Premium Outlets - plays host to luxury boutiques and stores selling everything from clothes and accessories to cosmetics and home essentials. Its world-class boutiques showcasing collections from prestigious local and international designers make for a truly memorable shopping experience. Add to all these a unbeatable prices, and a handful of trendy cafs and restaurants, and what youll get is one of the best shopping destinations in and around the Seattle. After you finish your shopping you will be picked up and will be delivered directly to your hotel in Seattle.

All our vehicles are fully licensed and insured. We are happy to provide child seats in our cars for all ages upon request. Vehicles are clean inside and outside; our drivers are well-dressed and unfailingly attentive to our guests. They speak English. They will greet you with a name sign and will help with luggage.
